room_title: Escape room "The Chicken Wing Sting" by Queen City Escape in Buffalo
room_description: Good citizens of Buffalo! Detective Logan Barry needs your help! The nefarious Wing-Burgler has gone back in time to steal the Buffalo Chicken Wing. Now everyone knows them as “Cincinnati Wings”! You have to set the record straight and reclaim our heritage! Do you have what it takes to crack this caper and solve the mystery of the first Buffalo Escape Room designed specifically for WNY?
